<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4855] DistributedUpdateProcessor doesn&apos;t check for peer sync</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4855</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DistributedUpdateProcessor has the following code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; isReplayOrPeersync = (cmd.getFlags() &amp;amp; (UpdateCommand.REPLAY | UpdateCommand.REPLAY)) != 0;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be replaced by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; isReplayOrPeersync = (cmd.getFlags() &amp;amp; (UpdateCommand.REPLAY | UpdateCommand.PEER_SYNC)) != 0;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
